的不是这个，\n而是那天回去之后的事。\n莉莎同学联系我，邀我去赏花","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev74-ep3-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"诶，莉莎同学？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev74-ep3-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"兰","body":"嗯。那时我立刻回复说我要去。\n之后问了一下，听说同行的人是罕见的阵容，\n我就有点担心了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev74-ep3-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"兰","body":"有彩同学、松原同学、麻弥同学，\n还有莉莎同学和我。最后是我们这几个人\n一起去赏花的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev74-ep3-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"真的是很罕见的阵容啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"chara